modName: Sword Art Online A Skyrim Expansion
summary: This Mod will be a quest line expansion to Skyrim inspired by the Japanese Anime Sword Art Online, this mod is a parody of some of the events within the show. The mod Adds Dungeons, armor, weapons, follower (marriageable) as well as voice acting.
descriptionHtml: Longer in depth to be added as the Mod comes further along in the development process.
author: Cole Andrew and Forest
